      "text": "星見プロはお人好しってだけじゃなく\nファンとの距離がとにかく近いですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Productions is not only good-natured\nbut also very close to the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
