      "text": "今は、ライブ中のファンとの距離を近くしたり\nMCで砕けた内容を提案してきたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ we are closer to the fans during live performances‚\nand you suggest more informal MC content. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.4333343334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_02_03-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "パフォーマンスは大事にしながらも\n少しずつ親しみやすさを出すように仕向けてますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think we are trying to make their performances more\nintimate‚ while keeping the importance of the performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
