      "text": "まぁ、私達もアイデアが気に食わなければ躊躇なく\n却下するので、これからも自由に提案してみて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if we don't like an idea‚ we won't hesitate to reject it either‚\nso please feel free to continue to make suggestions!",
        "id": ""
